init_text: A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She's unaware that she's actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who's fallen for her, and is certain he's going to get it right this time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He realizes that he loves her enough to start changing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He's learning that he doesn't need to change his appearance, but he does need to start changing his behavior.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He starts to find out what makes him tick.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He's no longer constantly trying to change himself for her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She comes over and talks to him.
